@node Installation
@chapter Installation

Nael's LSP-based features (via Eglot or lsp-mode), require Lean version 4 to be @uref{https://lean-lang.org/install/manual/, installed}.

If you prefer third-party lsp-mode over Emacs' built-in LSP-client Eglot, install @code{nael-lsp}.  You might need to install lsp-mode beforehand.

